{"tid":289315,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"市民用八達通乘港鐵　每程回贈3%","createTime":"2017-06-19T01:27:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-19T05:11:17.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"10bd997fd22c19e3a8b90c72a5a739addf068264","tid":289315,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T01:27:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20060883&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170619\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20060883%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170619&d=qCyVfIZAWkoOQgf583wEdrr9WXPazFMcT8p8rn878U0%3D&h=47d1fccd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20060883%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170619&h=03209c99\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20060883&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170619</a><br />\n<br />\n市民用八達通乘港鐵　每程回贈3%<br />\n<br />\n要聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n港鐵乘客昨日起用八達通乘車時可獲每程3%車費回贈，為期半年。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港鐵昨日起向使用八達通的乘客，提供每程3%車費回贈，為期半年，至12月17日。以荃灣到尖沙嘴為例，成人八達通收費為10.1元，半年的優惠期內，每程收費則降至9.7元，變相減價4毫。使用長者八達通乘客亦可受惠，每程車費由現時2元減至1.9元。<br />\n立法會鐵路事宜小組委員會主席田北辰稱，港鐵提供的回贈不是減價，又斥港鐵年年賺錢，即使推出票價優惠，但票價仍一直上升。他斥政府只顧增加鐵路資源，忽略改善其他交通運輸，倡長遠應增加巴士數目，巴士公司也可推出面值低於700元的月票「全港通」，為市民提供乘車優惠。<br />\n<br />\n機場快綫加價<br />\n<br />\n此外，機場快綫自1998年通車以來昨首次加價。新收費下，由香港或九龍站前往機場，成人八達通票價將一律加10元，新收費分別為110元及100元。<br />\n單程票加幅更高，香港或九龍站前往機場，成人票加15元，新票價分別為115及105元；青衣到機場成人八達通及單程票，新票價為65及70元，分別加價5元及10元。港鐵亦推出暑假優惠，即日起至八月底，小童用八達通可免費乘搭機場快綫，長者就有半價優惠。&nbsp;<br />\n■記者譚靜雯<br />\n<br />\n97年主權移交至今，香港前進還是倒退？「蘋果」與你細數廿載風雨。<br />\n【回歸二十年】專頁：&nbsp;<a href=\"http://hksar20.appledaily.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhksar20.appledaily.com.hk&d=qCyVfIZAWkoOQgf583wEdrr9WXPazFMcT8p8rn878U0%3D&h=f0c76780\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hksar20.appledaily.com.hk</a>￼"},{"pid":"aeb1716567ccd42a61d53afc3c3daeed36d3c886","tid":289315,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T01:28:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170619/large/1497801535_fbe6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170619%2Flarge%2F1497801535_fbe6.jpg&h=258f2521&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港鐵乘客昨日起用八達通乘車時可獲每程3%車費回贈，為期半年。"},{"pid":"6a3ea6238bd3c890a5c3420c7bbeb1c8e76ddf72","tid":289315,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T01:40:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我第二程九折明明抵啲"},{"pid":"4c875ac4dd33ffc90283d9706f698e5ead710fc8","tid":289315,"uid":114097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T01:41:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多！謝！狗！鐵！<br />\n跪低叩三下頭先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86b68a8cc5230551e8e49e32c0de8b39421c9a4d","tid":289315,"uid":32723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T01:42:45.000Z","msg":"真係多謝哂港鐵<br />\n可以平坐港鐵.<br />\n<br />\n唔洗迫巴士啦.........<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你啦, 平個3%? 十蚊都只係三毫子, 想點呀你.<br />\n<br />\n回程九折好過啦"},{"pid":"1ce46210d88251b43368b33f3eb3e7ba1d5a37d7","tid":289315,"uid":84081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T01:43:19.000Z","msg":"都會票又唔見有97折<br />\n<br />\n係咪潤鳩香港人97要收返?"},{"pid":"cd04c87f0e89826c283f89e65eba4960694c0bcb","tid":289315,"u